      "content": "I see. So you're saying the climate side is essentially the priority? Even if it means certain groups have to pay a higher percentage of their income just to get to work? I'm just trying to understand if there's a way to view the economic impact as a dealbreaker rather than just something that needs \"mitigation.\"",
